{
  "stem": "935.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what are they going to do to me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, she was German nationality, even though she was fluent in Dutch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "German passport.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are they going to do to me?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First she started with going out on Friday buying kosher chickens for old frightened Jews who didn't dare to go out anymore.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she lit the candles, and she did the shopping for them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then she was always in houses where she wasn't supposed to be anymore, like ours.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Wasn't allowed anymore.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She came to the theater.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was just a game.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after I was arrested for the first time, things became much more difficult.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she started building a little place in her-- she-- way up in the attic.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She had a tiny little room, a hiding place for Jews, which was impossible because her room itself was so very tiny.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But she had built a contraption in her closet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was ingenious.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was a closed up attic behind it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You couldn't sit the war out up there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But for a while, there were quite a lot, when they were running away, they went-- ended up at, as I always said, Margit's room at the top.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It took 64 stairs to get up to her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that was what was the safety, so called.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because by the time somebody rang the bell and somebody opened the door, and you could hear the creaking stairs, you had time to get into the hiding place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Now at that day, when I came home, I didn't go to my place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I went to her up there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And first of all, there were already two other girls there, which I didn't-- I mean, I knew them, but I didn't know them.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
